---
/**
 * Author bio box for blog posts.
 * E-E-A-T trust signals: credentials, experience, authority, social proof.
 */
---

<div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-start">
  <div class="flex-shrink-0">
    <a href="/about/" class="block">
      <img
        src="/blog/thumbnails/luca-berton-author.jpg"
        alt="Luca Berton — AI & Cloud Advisor, Docker Captain"
        width="80"
        height="80"
        loading="lazy"
        class="rounded-full w-20 h-20 object-cover border-2 border-gray-200"
        onerror="this.outerHTML='<div class=\'w-20 h-20 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold\'>LB</div>'"
      />
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">
      <a href="/about/" class="hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">Luca Berton</a>
    </h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-blue-700 font-semibold mt-0.5">AI & Cloud Advisor · Docker Captain · KubeCon Speaker</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
      18+ years in enterprise infrastructure. Author of
      <a href="/books/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">8 technical books</a>,
      creator of <a href="https://www.ansiblepilot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Ansible Pilot</a>
      (1M+ YouTube views, 648K site users). Former Red Hat engineer. Speaker at
      <a href="/kubecon/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">KubeCon EU 2026</a> and
      <a href="/blog/red-hat-summit-2026/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Red Hat Summit 2026</a>.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-3 items-center">
      <a href="https://calendly.com/lucaberton/" class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 text-sm font-bold transition">📅 Book a Call</a>
      <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucaberton/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-700 transition text-sm font-medium">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/lucaberton.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-500 transition text-sm font-medium">Bluesky</a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@BertonLuca" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-600 transition text-sm font-medium">YouTube</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-600 text-sm font-medium transition">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
